3a) I chose nano
3b) CTRL+O and Enter key to save and CTRL-X to exit the editor
3c) 	
	i) CTRL-SHIFT-V can be used to paste text
	ii) Triple clicking a line marks it and can be copy pasted with CTRL+SHIFT+C/V
	iii) It is possible to search in nano by pressing CTRL+W, entering a keyword and pressing enter

